{"tid":1896700,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果取消功能組別邊個得益最大","createTime":"2020-02-25T09:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T10:06:20.000Z","uid":339472,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41dfd2b608fdcfe51212a08f223a0ad1332304cb","tid":1896700,"uid":339472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"純討論，唔係批評抗爭方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問問大家點睇<br />\n如果取消左功能組別，其實邊個派別嘅人最開心/得益最大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次運動泛民成績都有目共睹，雖然未至於做得好Top但總算冇好似雨傘咁柒，特別係後生果班泛民都跟得比較貼<br />\n所以如果假設今年係冇左功能組別，成個立法會我假設係泛民奪大部分議席應該冇錯？<br />\n啫係好似前排區議會咁，至少應該有6：4比<br />\n如果取消到功能組別係泛民最開心嘅，咁調番轉諗邊個最唔想取消功能組別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（敵人反對嘅事我地係咪應該支持？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非引戰 純討論 不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><strong></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"ef5a03cdd69e8d08eea1de9993885964b3a4934e","tid":1896700,"uid":38526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"取消功能組別香港人最開心"},{"pid":"e207aeab75fba3aee21c0f568478324a14e36d54","tid":1896700,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"借ac:是咁的，我係西環駱先生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1896677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1896677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf1b645b96277b5deb20fcc89225145695829e2b","tid":1896700,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef5a03cdd69e8d08eea1de9993885964b3a4934e","tid":1896700,"uid":38526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:48:18.000Z","msg":"取消功能組別香港人最開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"佢都係咁話"},{"pid":"45c6e7c38214408ca26f9a407275275341472f76","tid":1896700,"uid":339472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T09:50